Kubernetes Setup:
==================
1. Start with minicube to setup single node setup.
     https://kubernetes.io/docs/getting-started-guides/minikube/
2. https://github.com/kubernetes/community/blob/master/contributors/devel/development.md
3. https://thenewstack.io/tutorial-configuring-ultimate-development-environment-kubernetes/
4. https://abhishek-tiwari.com/local-development-environment-for-kubernetes-using-minikube/
5. https://blog.giantswarm.io/getting-started-with-a-local-kubernetes-environment/
6. https://github.com/kubernetes/community/blob/master/contributors/devel/vagrant.md
7. https://kubernetes.io/docs/imported/community/devel/   (overall developer guide)
8. https://github.com/kubernetes/community/blob/master/contributors/devel/running-locally.md  (setup using hack/local-up-cluster.sh)
9. Manual Installation:
	 https://github.com/kelseyhightower/kubernetes-the-hard-way
10. Multinode Installation using Kubeadm
    	https://kubernetes.io/docs/setup/independent/
	   https://www.mirantis.com/blog/how-install-kubernetes-kubeadm/

